# ---- OSS / Cloud split (per `00-vision-and-principles.md` §6) ----
# The OSS workspace (this directory) is the public open-source runtime.
# The cloud-heavy trait impls live in `kx-cloud/` and are PRIVATE — they will
# be developed in their own (separate, private) git repository nested inside
# this subdirectory when P5.5 begins. Until then, the directory holds only a
# stubbed Cargo workspace as an architectural breadcrumb. NEVER commit
# kx-cloud contents to the OSS repo.
kx-cloud/

